snippet.title: Epstein 2 - Steam Offical Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Join Detective Michael on his psychological horror adventure to gather evidence on Epstein's dark island and find his mother. In this single-player game, carefully read the notes, collect equipment to protect yourself from the attackers.Find Danold Trump and Epstein and learn the truth.

Steam:https://store.steampowered.com/app/3029230/Epstein_2/
